            "title": "下城門水塘男子車內燒炭亡 生前疑工作問題不開心",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"下城門水塘男子車內燒炭亡。黎志偉攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/3dd75050e01e77564ecccfd1b4f75cb5/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250222/_2025022202313941883.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">下城門水塘男子車內燒炭亡。黎志偉攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>下城門水塘發生燒炭自殺案。今日（22日）凌晨零時許，警方接獲報案，一名男子在下城門水塘停車場昏迷於私家車內，救援人員到場後，當場證實男子不治。車內乘客位上放有一盆燒過的炭。\n\n</p>\n<p>現場消息指，死者年約40歲，昨晚開始失聯，妻子一直打他的電話無人接聽。警方發現遺體後，事主親友相繼到場，神情哀傷。警方將遺體移出車外，並用綠色帳蓬遮蓋。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4096369/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方發現遺體後，事主親友相繼到場。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e2c21218a4457b710f563c5a0bcd09d0/2025-02/4_19.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方發現遺體後，事主親友相繼到場。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4096370/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方發現遺體後，事主親友相繼到場。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/300165843afdc976f9734959ac95f7fb/2025-02/1_15.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方發現遺體後，事主親友相繼到場。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4096371/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方發現遺體後，事主親友相繼到場。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b4ba1163906d52069d9a9f3dc146196c/2025-02/2_32.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方發現遺體後，事主親友相繼到場。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4096372/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方將遺體移出車外，並用綠色帳蓬遮蓋。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/26ab380a141c646eca43b2028f2564d8/2025-02/Screenshot_2025-02-21_at_6_12_07_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方將遺體移出車外，並用綠色帳蓬遮蓋。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4096373/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現場為下城門水塘停車場。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f96d5810feb7489d978b794e0adf0d66/2025-02/6_19.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現場為下城門水塘停車場。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>據了解，死者生前疑工作問題不開心。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
